{"tid":204531,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《雷神3》預告狂破迪士尼點擊紀錄 稱霸漫威系列作品","createTime":"2017-04-17T06:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T14:03:41.000Z","uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2a6409c8b35200f52109cc3121cfac2e598028","tid":204531,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"由漫威影業推出的強檔續集《雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏》（Thor: Ragnarok），本周一釋出首支預告，24小時內便突破1.36億次的點擊率，不僅創下漫威電影最高紀錄，也打破了迪士尼電影紀錄，相當驚人。<br />\n迪士尼電影預告的24小時內最高點擊率紀錄，是先前由真人版《美女與野獸》創下的1.27億次，而迪士尼旗下的漫威影業紀錄保持者則是《美國隊長3：英雄內戰》的9400萬次，目前這兩個紀錄都已被《雷神索爾3》輕鬆打破，最大的原因還是歸功於預告呈現的歡樂風格。<br />\n<br />\n老老柒柒佢個預告真係幾鬼馬<br />\nloop左幾次"},{"pid":"80f7bdbaf3ff226ce8c5a0d1b3c6df8aa4102616","tid":204531,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v7MGUNV8MxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv7MGUNV8MxU&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c9b4eac4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v7MGUNV8MxU</a><br />\n真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3f3ddbcc198729b938a244bf00c47aa038720f","tid":204531,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"最怕套野雷聲大乳點少"},{"pid":"17ba05445df2d1c4ed2975ee626f0c61e4fdad87","tid":204531,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"Yeah!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ae50baa5d8844e2655f365ab4b5a3aa48efefb","tid":204531,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"798eba9a97f1eff4f287f6823a8bd2c9de129a31","tid":204531,"uid":13987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"<b